%p Watergoal is an app for anyone who is interested in getting hydrated. Water is an important staple of a healthy lifestyle and many of us miss out on the great benefits. With Watergoal you can set your desired number of glasses of water to drink within a given day and keep track of your progress on your quest to hydration!
